Introduction

Jimin N J.Don (Korean: 지민 엔 제이던; Japanese: ジミンエンジェイデン) was a co-ed sub-unit formed by FNC Entertainment. Composed by AOA's Jimin and J.Don (Seunghyub) of N.Flying, the duo debuted on April 28, 2015, with the digital single "N Project #1 God."

Following Jimin's departure from AOA and the agency, it is assumed that the group has disbanded.
